## When User Has Issues

1. **"Configuration not found"** → `npm run setup`
2. **"Jira integration disabled"** → `npm run setup`, enable Jira
3. **"API key not found"** → Check `.env` file, re-run setup
4. **"Cluster not accessible"** → Verify `agent/config/user-config.json`

## Summary

This is a **configuration-driven** validation system. The user configures once (`npm run setup`), then validates any bug with one command (`npm run validate:jira ACM-XXXXX`). No custom code per bug.
